title: Duke Nukem: Land of the Babes playthrough -- Part 2
description: Really short game, but pretty good. Improved on Time to Kill in some ways, but had slightly worse levels I think. Overall, not the worst game of all time, probably not even the worst in the duke franchise, but nothing amazing.
